Author: carrotlime
Text: Right? Literally eaten ~500 and exercised my ass off since jan 1 and was so psyched only to binge yesterday 🙃

Author: wheresmywinegums
Text: I had to “clean out my fridge” today to make room for all the healthy groceries I bought.   Eating a container of leftover birthday cake icing on top of 5 homemade donuts leftover from Christmas from my grandma was exactly the right way to do that amirite🙄  = I feel you big time. I restricted so well all week and then blew it big time. Of course.
